{
  "stem": "16503.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the wintertime, we were skaters, so the parents or somebody flooded the volleyball, you know, field, and we skated there and then went into the hutch and had a hot chocolate and then we walked home.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was very good for us, because that was our-- our world, Hagibor, it was called.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was for that time-- time period, it was our world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it made us a part of a unit, which was starting to learn that being together and-- and friendship as such, not only a friendship of being in school, because that in the end I wouldn't call friendship.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was real acquaintances.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This was starting the era in my life of deep connection, of friendships of completely different kind, and which lasted for a long time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Unfortunately, most of the people which I was friends with died during the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the point where-- where the feeling of togetherness and-- and loyalty and truthfulness started to mean something and was an honorable thing to apply, and that was where we were learning it in a way where we played volleyball.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The older ones played volleyball.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were running track or doing gymnastics and somersaults or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as far as I know, it lasted-- I don't-- well, when I left, it was still there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, until I went to Theresienstadt, was called up for the transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that was the Jewish community in Prague were under the SS or whomever they were reporting to.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were told that on this particular day so many people have got to go into a transport.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now it was up-- as far as I understand, I might be wrong.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had to take the names out of a hat.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
